<A NAME="Cameron - Some useful ideas"> </A>
<P>To produce black and white illustrations for papers,try
<pre>
colour c black
colour h black
colour n black
colour o black
colour bond all white
ball all unfil
ball h fill
colour back grey
ELLIP
C
N
O
ELLIP
TYPE
ALL
4
CONN
TAPER
3
VIEW
</pre><p><BR>
<P>To hack up a packing diagram, cutting out most and just keeping a bit,
try (all on one line)
<pre>
EXCLUDE ALL INCLUDE AREA
</pre><p><BR>
Then use the mouse to draw round the bit you want to keep.
